# Random Tables

## Mountains

### Weather Table

| d6+X | Weather                                                                                                     |
| ---- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| 1    | A terrible blizzard strikes. Visibility is nearly nothing, movement slows, it is dark, and it is very cold. |
| 2    | The temperature plummets. Blue sky, but deathly cold. Need fire or to keep moving.                          |
| 3    | Snow falls. Movement slows, and it is colder.                                                               |
| 4    | It is cloudy and cold.                                                                                      |
| 5    | Blue sky.                                                                                                   |
| 6    | The temperature warms up. Snow is melting.                                                                  |

