## Jungles

### Weather Table

| d6+X | Weather                                                                                                                                           |
| ---- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| 1    | A powerful downpour comes down. Feet begin to rot, and food and rations go bad. Navigation is hard, visibility is terrible. Flash flood possible. |
| 2    | A powerful downpour comes down. Feet begin to rot, and food and rations go bad. Navigation is hard, visibility is terrible. Flash flood possible. |
| 3    | Sweltering heat requires twice as much water. Heat stroke and heat exhaustion must be avoided.                                                    |
| 4    | Sweltering heat requires twice as much water. Heat stroke and heat exhaustion must be avoided.                                                    |
| 5    | A light drizzle keeps things damp                                                                                                                 |
| 6    | Blue sky                                                                                                                                          |

