## Oceans

### Weather Table

| d6+X | Weather                                                                                          |
| ---- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| 1    | A terrible storm strikes, potentially driving you off course, and attracting deep sea creatures. |
| 2    | A heavy fog rolls in, making navigation impossible.                                              |
| 3    | A storm strikes, making navigation stop and movement stall.                                      |
| 4    | All wind dies.                                                                                   |
| 5    | A light breeze leads to slow but steady progress.                                                |
| 6    | Strong, pleasant winds push the boat onwards.                                                    |

### Event Table

| d100 | Event                                                                                                                                                                                     |
| ---- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| 1    | A quadruple rainbow is spotted. It leads to one of the four keys of light, which unlock passage to the sun and stars.                                                                     |
