| 8    | The boat hits a reef, becoming stuck.                                                                                                                                                     |
| 9    | The giant barnacle covered back of a leviathan surfaces nearby.                                                                                                                           |
| 10   | Flying fish soar onto the boat. They come in a multitude of colors.                                                                                                                       |
| 11   | A whirlpool is spotted ahead. If sucked in, you are propelled to another kingdom beneath the sea.                                                                                         |
| 12   | A merchant ship is being boarded by pirates.                                                                                                                                              |
| 13   | Debris from a concluded ship battle floats about.                                                                                                                                         |
| 14   | An abandoned merchant ship floats past, filled with riches. Why isn't there anyone aboard?                                                                                                |
